{"type": "article", "id": 22251, "title": "手提式伞架", "description": "", "date": "2016-02-15T07:30:16Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 17, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607105936FPUXsS3CNnAcTq2K.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这款放在室内的铝制伞架来自澳大利亚设计工作室 DesignByThem 和悉尼设计师 Seaton Mckeon。它的外形像一个长方体，可以放在房间的转角处而不会太占用空间。伞架的中间有一个提手方便移动，类似于口袋提手的设计，也将伞架划分成两半，下面的漏孔以方便将水滴在盒子里再集中清理。可以选择黑、白和明亮的金黄色，售价 330 澳元，<a href=\"http://www.designbythem.com/products/alfred-umbrella-stand\">这里是购买链接</a>。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607105934u2BENrDMskFZ5HhY.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607105935cXyv7GEPix0C9ROd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607105935ycrh70wxZ5Pvj43u.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607105936cP354Y9AhO6Wtl2R.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607105936e0dgatN8vzZ3PD1L.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n\n"}